content: Hi! I'm trying to get a callgrind profile of rustc, and followed the steps from https://github.com/rust-lang/rustc-perf/tree/master/collector#profiling. All the rust symbols come out mangled in the profile however (screenshot). I might have missed a step and if so I'm sorry, but is there a way to demangle these?
The current master of valgrind should support demangling of the new rust symbol mangling scheme.
Ah, so valgrind-3.16.1 from debian is probably too old then
